@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Configure System

|Administrator|
start
:Open System Configuration Menu;

|Frontend|
:Display System Settings;

|Administrator|
:Modify Configuration Settings;

|Frontend|
:Validate Configuration Data;

if (Configuration Valid?) then (Yes)

    |Backend|
    :Process Configuration Changes;
    :Save Configuration to Database;

    |Frontend|
    :Display Configuration Updated Message;

    |Administrator|
    :Review Updated Settings;

    stop

else (No)

    |Frontend|
    :Display Validation Error;

    |Administrator|
    :Correct Configuration Data;

endif

@enduml